可以让他看到120度的视野
208
00:08:51,533 --> 00:08:54,233
usually the driver enters through the hatch up front
通常司机从前面的舱门进去
209
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:57,133
but if needed the driver can climb into the turret
但如果需要，司机可以爬进炮塔
210
00:08:57,666 --> 00:09:00,066
